---
layout: page
title: "Notas"
description: "Pensamentos curtos, links interessantes e atualizações rápidas."
permalink: "{% if pagination.pageNumber > 0 %}/notes/page/{{ pagination.pageNumber + 1 }}/{% else %}/notes/{% endif %}"
date: Last Modified
pagination:
  data: collections.notes
  size: 12
---

<h1 class="mb-6 p-name font-bold text-brand-red-500 text-3xl">Notas</h1>
<p>Ideias curtas e fáceis de conectar. Cada nota tem seu próprio link permanente.</p>

<div class="h-feed">
  <div class="gap-4 grid grid-cols-1">
    {% for note in pagination.items %}
    <article
      class="flex flex-col shadow-sm hover:shadow-md p-6 border border-brand-gray-200 rounded-2xl transition-shadow">
      <time datetime="{{ note.data.pubDate | toISOString }}"
        class="mb-4 font-semibold text-brand-red-500 text-xs uppercase dt-published">
        {{ note.data.pubDate | formatDate('DD/MM/YYYY') }}
      </time>

      <div class="max-w-none e-content grow prose">
        {{ note.content | safe }}
      </div>

      {% if note.data.tags and note.data.tags.length > 0 %}
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-6 pt-4 border-brand-gray-300 border-t">
        {% for tag in note.data.tags %}
        {% if tag !== "notes" %}
        <span class="p-category font-bold text-brand-red-500 text-xs transition-colors cursor-default">#{{ tag }}</span>
        {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      {% endif %}
    </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</div>

